RiskDisclosure.RiskDescription: This contract carries significant risks, including credit risk, interest rate risk, and liquidity risk.
RiskDisclosure.Disclosure: Party 2 should consult its own financial, legal, accounting, and tax advisors about the risks associated with this contract.

OrdinaryCourseOfBusiness.Description: In the ordinary course of their business, Party 1 or its affiliates or subsidiaries may affect transactions for their own account or for the account of their customers.
OrdinaryCourseOfBusiness.Disclaimer: Neither Party 1 nor its affiliates or subsidiaries is obliged to take into account the circumstances of the parties to this contract or act in a manner that is favorable to them.

PotentialConflictsOfInterest.Description: Potential conflicts of interest may exist in the structure and operation of this contract and the course of the normal business activities of Party 1 or its affiliates or subsidiaries.

UnderlyingExposure.Description: This contract has been entered into to hedge the risk arising out of the underlying exposure of Party 2, which is a USD 10,000,000 fixed rate loan maturing on or after 2007-09-06.

PurposeOfTheTransaction.Description: The purpose of this contract is to convert the fixed rate USD liability of Party 2 into a floating rate liability with the view that future interest rates will be lower than currently projected.

ScenarioAnalysis.Description: The following scenario analysis is provided for illustrative and convenience purposes only and should not be relied upon by Party 2.
ScenarioAnalysis.Assumptions: The analysis assumes various levels of USD SOFR-COMPOUND and shows the resultant cash flow gain/loss to Party 2.

MarkToMarketMTMSensitivityAnalysis.Description: The following MTM analysis is provided for illustrative and convenience purposes only and should not be relied upon by Party 2.
MarkToMarketMTMSensitivityAnalysis.Analysis: The analysis shows the changes in the MTM due to parallel shifts in the USD SOFR-COMPOUND curve.

LevelOfPricingVariablesAndImpactOfVariab.Description: The following analysis is provided for information and illustrative purposes only and should not be relied upon by Party 2.
LevelOfPricingVariablesAndImpactOfVariab.Analysis: The analysis shows the market level of primary market variables used in determining the price of this contract and their directional impact.

ValuationStatements.Description: Valuation statements in relation to this contract will be made available to Party 2 on the Optimize application present on Party 1's online platform, J.P.Morgan Markets.
